overview: March 29th, 2009 :: The King Of Trios tournament reaches its climax, and the Rey de Voladores is crowned when Kota Ibushi tangles with Player Dos! The annual Tag Team Gauntlet match is a featured attraction, and non-tournament action steals the spotlight as Austin Aries fights Eddie Kingston, and Arik Cannon wrestles El Generico!
title: Chikara King Of Trios 2009 - Night 3
